{"tid":971391,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【流亡泰國前總理】他信、英祿兄妹 高調現身廣東梅州祭祖","createTime":"2019-01-06T14:57:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-08T03:25:30.000Z","uid":28765,"like":15,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"7d8dcdc510f2ea121bfb959d2ae503601285252b","tid":971391,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T14:57:40.000Z","msg":"流亡海外的泰國前總理他信及英祿兄妹，昨日（5日）早上現身「家鄉」廣東梅州豐順縣探親及祭祖。一眾鄉親熱烈歡迎，塔下村邱氏宗祠前金獅起舞，彩旗飄揚，鞭炮齊鳴，鼓樂喧天，現場十分熱鬧。<br />\n據內地傳媒報道，他信與英祿是第四代泰國華僑，是客家人後裔，兩人曾於2005及2014年到梅州尋根。<br />\n資料顯示，英祿被指於2011至2014年出任泰國總理期間，推出大米補貼政策，令泰國損失80億美元，因而被控瀆職罪，2017年9月被判囚5年，但她在判刑前失蹤，遭泰國政府通緝。而他信曾3度當選泰國總理，2006年因被指涉貪，泰國選民響應反對派呼籲在選舉中投下大量棄權票，他信逼於壓力下台，就在轉任看守總理期間，泰國發生政變，他信最後流亡海外。<br />\n2018年2月農曆新年，網傳他信及英祿曾出現在北京街頭，兩人還通過網絡向泰國人送上春節祝福。<br />\n搜狐網  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190105/large/1546702681_2580.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190105%2Flarge%2F1546702681_2580.jpg&h=009ef280&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n他信與英祿兄妹，現身廣東梅州祭祖<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190105/large/1546702681_c1a6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190105%2Flarge%2F1546702681_c1a6.jpg&h=a8dbaeb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n他信與英祿，在廣東梅州大受歡迎。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190105/large/1546702681_abfd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190105%2Flarge%2F1546702681_abfd.jpg&h=d1f6b34c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n兩人與一眾鄉親合照。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190106/59109462\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190106%2F59109462&d=Yn22%2BRciTYZw5tTnbpOTr4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=69290f4c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190106%2F59109462&h=0440d44d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190106/59109462</a>"},{"pid":"95dc55b249a6a22ce8f92752fa014973ee38a4e2","tid":971391,"uid":141151,"like":56,"dislike":0,"score":56,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T15:10:40.000Z","msg":"秦國是中国不可分割的一部分<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c77adf79febf46c8e0677368b5e373852ae163ad","tid":971391,"uid":34773,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T15:33:26.000Z","msg":"通輯犯可以周圍走, 泰國真係廢"},{"pid":"222947670d595273b4e83ef3d5e84cd64e7986aa","tid":971391,"uid":100131,"like":1,"dislike":32,"score":-31,"quote":{"pid":"95dc55b249a6a22ce8f92752fa014973ee38a4e2","tid":971391,"uid":141151,"like":56,"dislike":0,"score":56,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T15:10:40.000Z","msg":"秦國是中国不可分割的一部分<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T15:34:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 秦國早已滅亡"},{"pid":"21d5a976802e3257b4cad836156a2c8053262348","tid":971391,"uid":7814,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T15:51:20.000Z","msg":"住喺大陸真係有陣柒味<br />\n<br />\n唔好話咩去泰國已經溝淡咗<br />\nor 有化妝所以睇落好d (PS 英祿後面果條個樣好似唔差)<br />\n<br />\n淨係講個髮型，d 大媽頭真係全中國一撚樣<br />\n- 大媽冬菇頭<br />\n- 貼服型陳方安生頭<br />\n<br />\n男人衣著永遠都係得2款<br />\n- 鬆拋拋2粒鈕有領單色恤衫 + 西裝褸/羽絨 + 西褲<br />\n- 高樽領 + 西裝褸/羽絨 + 西褲"},{"pid":"0c77b9412e293c529b8113014f542f42e6440729","tid":971391,"uid":115096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T16:04:34.000Z","msg":"似乎冇國家接受泰國引渡令"},{"pid":"eb7c97384a6c62eb2ec9f1be69c7987b379d9193","tid":971391